com.ibm.team.build.common.model

Interface IBuildConfigurationElement


  • public interface IBuildConfigurationElement
    Defines configuration data as part of a IBuildDefinition or IBuildEngine.
    Since:
    0.6

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static java.lang.String CONFIGURATION_PROPERTY_LICENSE_ID
      Presence of this configuration property in the element indicates that a license check will occur when a build definition containing this configuration element is saved and this configuration element has been added or modified.
      static java.lang.String CONFIGURATION_PROPERTY_VARIABLE_SUBSTITUTION
      Presence of this configuration property in the element indicates that variable references in this element's configuration property values will be substituted by the Jazz build engine.

    • Field Detail

      • CONFIGURATION_PROPERTY_VARIABLE_SUBSTITUTION

        static final java.lang.String CONFIGURATION_PROPERTY_VARIABLE_SUBSTITUTION
        Presence of this configuration property in the element indicates that variable references in this element's configuration property values will be substituted by the Jazz build engine. Variable references have the form ${variableName}
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • CONFIGURATION_PROPERTY_LICENSE_ID

        static final java.lang.String CONFIGURATION_PROPERTY_LICENSE_ID
        Presence of this configuration property in the element indicates that a license check will occur when a build definition containing this configuration element is saved and this configuration element has been added or modified. A license check will also occur when a build request is issued for a build definition containing this configuration element.
        Since:
        0.8
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
